The assignment is an audio-based project that uses something electronic or electromechanical in some way.

In lecture we showed the dance between technical discovery, media and instrumentation, subculture appropriation, 
and artistic re-appropriation. What noises distract you? What is the sound of a place you're interested in, and what
can you do with it? What's the sound of your internal monologue? Smartphones may be your friends here, but then so again might be Ithaca ReUse.
